<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>For You ❤️</title>

```html
<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #333;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4, #ffd1ff);
    background-size: 400% 400%;
    animation: romanticBg 12s ease infinite;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Animated background movement */
@keyframes romanticBg {
    0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
    100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
}

/* Floating hearts */
body::before {
    content: "❤️ ❤️ 💕 ❤️ 💖 💕 ❤️";
    position: fixed;
    top: -10px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 25px;
    opacity: 0.3;
    animation: floatHearts 12s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes floatHearts {
    0% {
        transform: translateY(-20px);
    }
    100% {
        transform: translateY(100vh);
    }
}

.container {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    text-align: center;
}
.photo-frame {
    margin: 30px auto;
    width: 320px;
    padding: 10px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 25px;
    box-shadow: 0px 10px 35px rgba(255, 77, 109, 0.4);
    transform: rotate(-2deg);
    transition: 0.4s;
}

.photo-frame:hover {
    transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.05);
}

.photo-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 20px;
}

.caption {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #ff4d6d;
    font-style: italic;
}
  
h1 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 42px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff4d6d,
                 0 0 20px #ff4d6d,
                 0 0 30px #ff85a2;
}
   
.message {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0px 8px 30px rgba(255,77,109,0.25);
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.question {
    margin-top: 30px;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff4d6d;
}

.buttons {
    margin-top: 25px;
}

button {
    padding: 15px 35px;
    font-size: 20px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 30px;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin: 10px;
    transition: 0.3s;
}

button: hover {
    transform: scale(1.1);
}

.yes {
    background: #ff4d6d;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px #ff4d6d;
}

.no {
    background: #666;
    color: white;
}

#response {
    margin-top: 25px;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff4d6d;
}
</style>
```

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Baby, I’m Sorry ❤️</h1>

    <div class="photo-frame">
        <img src="love.png" alt="Us Together ❤️">
        <div class="caption">Us... the way I always want us to be ❤️</div>
    </div>

    <div class="message">

       <p>
       Mujhe pata hai sirf “sorry” bolne se sab theek nahi hoga… 💔<br>
       Maine tujhe bahut hurt kiya hai, aur iska regret mujhe sach mein hai.<br>
       Shayad jo dard maine diya, uska ehsaas tujhe mujhse zyada hua hoga… aur yahi baat mujhe andar se todti hai.<br>
       Kabhi kabhi sochta hoon ki kaash waqt wapas aa jaye ⏳, toh shayad main tujhe woh dard kabhi na deta.
       </p>

       <p>
       Bas itna samajh le ki jo bhi hai, dil se hai ❤️<br>
       Mere emotions kabhi fake nahi the, aur na hi mera pyaar.<br>
       Shayad dikhane ka tareeka galat tha, shayad samjhaane mein kami reh gayi…<br>
       Par jo mehsoos karta hoon, woh hamesha sach tha.<br>
       Galtiyan meri thi… par meri mohabbat kabhi jhooti nahi thi.
       </p>

       <p>
       Main ghar par tab tak kuch nahi bata sakta jab tak meri job nahi lag jaati… 📌<br>
       Aur shaadi wali commitment bhi isliye nahi de paaya kyunki main kabhi tujhe jhooti umeed dekar hurt nahi karna chahta tha.<br>
       Main chahta tha ki jab bhi tere saamne koi wada rakhun, woh sirf lafzon ka nahi, haqeeqat ka ho 🤍<br>
       Isliye ruk raha tha… khud ko pehle itna kaabil banane ke liye ki tujhe bina darr ke apna sakun.
       </p>

       <p>
       Job toh main le lunga… kyunki uske bina na meri zindagi sambhalegi, na main woh future bana paunga jo main chahta hoon 📚<br>
       Bas tab tak yahi socha tha ki hum dono apne apne goals aur sapno par focus karein — tere comfort ke saath, bina kisi pressure ke ✨<br>
       Mujhe bhi apne exam par dhyaan dena hai, aur tujhe bhi apni zindagi ko us jagah tak le jaana hai jahan tu deserve karti hai.<br>
       Par sach yeh hai… itni responsibilities aur future ki tension ke beech bhi, mera dil tujhe alag nahi kar paata 🤍<br>
       Main chahta hoon ki main khud ko bhi sambhalun, apne future ko bhi, aur tujhe bhi us jagah rakhun jahan tu deserve karti hai — izzat, sukoon aur sachche pyaar ke saath.<br>
       Bas yahi sochta hoon… kya hum apne sapne sambhalte hue, ek dusre ka saath bhi nahi sambhal sakte?
       </p>

       <p>
       Sach kahun toh, aaj tak mujhe kisi ke liye aisi feelings nahi aayi… 🌙<br>
       Isliye samajhne mein bhi waqt lag gaya…<br>
       Par ab jab aayi hain, tab samajh aaya ki kisi ko dil se chahna kya hota hai.<br>
       Aur ab jab samjha hoon… toh darr lagta hai, tujhe kho dene ka 😔
       </p>

       <p>
       Mujhe teri awaaz sunne ka mann karta hai… 🎧<br>
       Tujhe dekhne ka mann karta hai… 👀<br>
       Tera gussa karna, tera ladna, tere nakhre, tera over cute banna, apni baat zabardasti manvana, teri nautanki… sab yaad aata hai 🥺<br>
       Sach bolun toh padhte waqt hi khud ko rok leta hoon, taki apne goal se divert na ho jaun…<br>
       Warna baaki har waqt tu mere dimaag aur dil mein rehti hai ❤️‍🩹
       </p>

       <p>
       Tere saath vibe bhi alag hi feel hoti hai… ✨<br>
       Natural, comfortable aur sachchi.<br>
       Aur agar qualities ki baat karun, toh mere liye tu best hai 🌸<br>
       Mujhe lagta hai hum saath mein bahut ache lagte… sirf dekhne mein nahi, samajhne mein bhi.
       </p>

       <p>
       Ek baat aur…<br>
       Main har cheez mein careless raha hoon 😞<br>
       Sach bolun toh mujhe kabhi kisi cheez ki care karna properly aaya hi nahi.<br>
       Shayad isi wajah se tujhe woh care nahi de paaya jo tujhe milni chahiye thi.<br>
       Aur us baat ka guilt mujhe rahega.
       </p>

       <p>
       Par agar tu sikhayegi, toh seekhne ki meri puri koshish rahegi 🤍<br>
       Ab tak bhi maine tujhse bahut kuch seekha hai… aur aage bhi bahut kuch seekhna chahta hoon.<br>
       Main perfect nahi hoon… par tere saath better banna chahta hoon 🌹<br>
       Shayad mere liye pyaar ka matlab bhi wahi hai — tere saath rehkar khud ko sudhaarna.
       </p>

       <p>
       Aur ek baat yaad rakhna — 💫<br>
       Mere liye tu kabhi koi option nahi thi, aur na kabhi hogi.<br>
       Tu meri “only one” hai ❤️<br>
       Jo beet gaya, usse wahi chhod dete hain…<br>
       Kyunki agar hum sach mein saath chalein, toh past sirf ek chapter hoga… aur future hum dono ka 🤝
       </p>

       <p>
       Bas itna jaanta hoon…<br>
       Main tujhe hurt karne ke liye nahi, tere saath chalne ke liye aaya tha ❤️<br>
       Aur aaj bhi wahi chahta hoon.
       </p>

    </div>

    <div class="question">
        Kya tu mujhe maaf karegi? ❤️
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">
        <button class="yes" onclick="showLove()">Yes</button>
        <button class="no" onclick="showNo()">No</button>
    </div>

<form action="https://formspree.io/f/xwvdeaop" method="POST">

<textarea name="message" placeholder="Write your reply here ❤️" required></textarea>

<br><br>

<button type="submit" class="yes">Send Reply ❤️</button>

</form>
    <div id="response"></div>

</div>

<script>
function showLove() {
    document.getElementById("response").innerHTML =
    "Thank you... ❤️ Main promise karta hu ki better banne ki puri koshish karunga.";
}

function showNo() {
    document.getElementById("response").innerHTML =
    "Main wait karunga... jab tak tera gussa kam nahi hota ❤️";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
```
